node.text: Add the latest #LEGO #SuperMario sets to your collection with the Boss Sumo Bro Topple Tower Expansion Set, Lakitu Sky World Expansion Set,  and the Reznor Knockdown Expansion Set available at #NintendoNYC for $29.99, $39.99, and $69.99!

node.text: Stop by #NintendoNYC and team up with your favorite character in the real world with this #LEGO Super Mario Adventures with Luigi Starter Course available now for $59.99, while supplies last!

node.text:
What are some perks of visiting Nintendo NY?

Scan your #MyNintendo QR Code to check-in with the kiosk at #NintendoNYC! Receive 100 My Nintendo Platinum Points that can be redeemed for cool rewards.

Check out the latest rewards here: https://my.nintendo.com/reward_categories

node.text:
Summer Vibes~ ☀️ 
 
Breeze by #NintendoNYC and pick up this fashionable #AnimalCrossing Fruit Icon Backpack for $29.99 or Fruit Icon Sling Bag for $49.99. Each bag has dedicated storage for your #NintendoSwitch system.

node.text:
On Friday, 7/16 fly on over to #NintendoNYC and purchase the Zelda & Loftwing #amiibo. 

This amiibo features two characters on a single base and can be used to travel between the surface and the sky in The Legend of #Zelda: #SkywardSwordHD.

node.text:
On Friday, 7/16 stop by #NintendoNYC to purchase The Legend of #Zelda: #SkywardSword HD specially-designed Joy-Con controllers for $79.99! 

The right Joy-Con controller is themed after the Master Sword, while the left features a Hylian Shield motif.
